302
00:49:20,960 --> 00:49:22,800
[SPEAKER_01] Trebala bi, da.

303
00:49:24,960 --> 00:49:25,599
[SPEAKER_01] Trebala bi, da.

304
00:49:25,840 --> 00:49:33,760
